{"tid":756872,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"狗狗不斷舔自己膝頭哥","createTime":"2018-07-26T10:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T11:42:45.000Z","uid":9938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2a849442d401faaafcc2326e2c5ac9ab821f8117","tid":756872,"uid":9938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:59:46.000Z","msg":"(借朋友Acc 開）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/185508_cada97e18f3cdc4cd65cdec630912fce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F185508_cada97e18f3cdc4cd65cdec630912fce.png&h=a1e62fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n狗仔以前斷過左腳好返 醫生話唔好比佢係太高既地方跳落地就唔會有咩大礙<br />\n<br />\n最近狗仔有時候會收起左腳跛行（大部份時間都正常）<br />\n最近發現佢成日舔自己左腳膝頭哥 舔到啲毛痴口水痴到硬哂 <br />\n有冇巴絲知道大概會係咩事 會盡快帶佢睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab60cffcb2103973a1d79c0bc398059cf00aed1","tid":756872,"uid":1060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:25:24.000Z","msg":"有冇做過菠蘿蓋手術？"},{"pid":"99165fc4686906e914a3b3561c06253d35c81262","tid":756872,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T11:42:45.000Z","msg":"🐩poodle<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}